Coal of Africa Says Vele Water Use License Suspended Following NGO Appeal

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-07-29T00:21:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/coal-of-africa-says-vele-water-use-license-suspended-following-ngo-appeal.html
Coal of Africa Ltd. (CZA)  said the
Integrated Water Use Licence for the Vele Colliery has been
suspended in terms of the South Africa National Water Act due to
an appeal to the Water Tribunal submitted by an NGO coalition.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  